To run this programm you need the following packages: 
bristol, python3, python3-tk

To install pyBristol just make the "install-sh"-script executable
and run it as root.

To unintall make the scrict "uninstall-sh" executable and run it.

=========
[INSTALL]
doc opt/pyBristol
gif opt/pyBristol
icon opt/pyBristol
pyBristol.py opt/pyBristol
default.conf opt/pyBristol
pyBristol usr/bin/
pyBristol.desktop /usr/share/applications/
pyBristol.svg usr/share/pixmaps/